        <table>
          <tr><th>WHAT</th><th>DOESN'T EXIST ON THIS PAGE</th></tr>
          <tr><td>Tab bar</td><td>❌ Status filtering is in sidebar nav + filter pills. NO tab bar above the table.</td></tr>
          <tr><td>View header</td><td>❌ Page identity comes from sidebar nav (active item "Purchase Orders").</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Bulk bar</td><td>❌ Only appears after checking rows (see Wireframe 3).</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Slideover</td><td>❌ Only appears after clicking a row (see Wireframe 4).</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Summary strip</td><td>❌ A single KPI line above the table replaces any heavy summary component.</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Prominent CTA</td><td>❌ "New PO" is accessed via sidebar action or + in filter area — not a big button.</td></tr>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
         3. GRID VIEW — ROW SELECTED (BULK BAR)
