          <tr><td>0 selected</td><td>Hidden. No bar at all.</td></tr>
          <tr><td>1+ selected</td><td>Appears at bottom of table. Dark translucent bar.</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Deselect all</td><td>Disappears immediately.</td></tr>
